dw.com
Database: Donations to German parties between 2013 and 2017
26.05.2018 • 16:05 • Authors: Ben Knight, Gianna-Carina Grün

Read the story based on this data here at DW.

This table holds data on major donations (a single donation larger than 50K euros) to a German party (only included CDU, CSU, SPD, Gruene, FDP and AfD) from January 2013 until September 2017.

Major donations are marked with type "g".

It also holds information on smaller donations to these parties (smaller than 50K, but in sum larger than 3K per year), based on the financial accounts of the parties from 2013 to 2015, which is the latest year available at publication date.

Smaller donations from the financial accounts are marked with type "r". These always have a date_received of yyyy-01-01, which was assigned during the automation process, but is not the real date when the donation was received, as this information is not available.

For further information on sourcing, cleaning and analysing the data, please see this github repository for reference.

In case you have questions or find errors, we'd highly appreciate if you get in touch: design.data[at]dw[dot]com
